    Photo by Anna Williams - May 1, 2023
  </div>
    </div>
    <div class="image">
      <img src="/public/images/lake2.jpg" alt="Third Slide">
      <div class="image-caption">
    Photo by Rachel Murray - June 10, 2023
  </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="buttons is-centered">
  <button class="prev arrow">&#10094;</button>
